hey, can someone help how to change to .rar?
I follow the steps but i canÂ´t find anything that says "folder options"?

#auguststaaf: If the file ending is already showing (that is, the name of the downloaded file ends with ".avi") you do not have to go through this step. Just click on the file name and change ".avi" to ".rar". If the file ending is not showing, change the settings under Tools (in the window menu)/Folder options. There are several tabs, choose View. Uncheck "Hide extensions for unknown file types". Then the file ending will show, allowing you to change it.
